717772f-a.title: Manhattan: Broadway - 174th Street
717772f-a.text:
Broadway, west side, from and including 174th to and including 175th Streets. The view also shows 174th Street, north side, from Broadway to but not including Ft. Washington Ave.
About 1926.
Browning Studios.
